		      Alright, Now Straight To The Checking,
			Let's Say We Now Have Both The Variable Defined
			Now we have to check if 'We have more money than the price'
			We'll use 'If Else' for these simple 2 choice situation. If there're more option, I'd recommend 'If Elseif'.
			>>>
		]]
