		Content = [[
			But when it comes to translating into languages or put it into various game engines, it may require some knowledge or profession. Take it slow, no need to actually rush, just make sure you're actually learning, not copying a tutorial one to one. but to consider your own approach after listening to the logic or result provided by the Ytbers or Scripters
			-Solivion 2024
